{"tid":387808,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"父親因買錯熱飲被毆打","createTime":"2017-09-05T02:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T05:08:36.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbfdb6eda048e31cd124f34783362cd9eef89201","tid":387808,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"沙田發生逆子打父母事件。昨晚11時許，水泉澳邨嶺泉樓一名18歲姓楊青年，叫83歲行動不便的老父替他落街買飯盒及凍飲。詎料老父回家後，青年發現父親買錯熱飲，他情緒激動，喝罵老父及母親(54歲)，並取起父親的拐杖襲擊兩老，兩老負傷逃至樓下大堂向保安員求助，由保安代為報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，將姓楊青年拘捕，涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害。而受傷的兩老則由救護車送院治理。據悉，涉案的楊男於2016年時，曾涉嫌打傷母親。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57168924&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57168924%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&d=5B7r%2BAZueykZiYDSZnkVXfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=042357a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57168924%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&h=a7fc0440\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57168924&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904</a>"},{"pid":"52bd98ff6a64ff53d92496de05535293a8347ce9","tid":387808,"uid":45280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:04:34.000Z","msg":"仲以係用生果刀隔離條法包"},{"pid":"9f7a32d021e2c9c11e51dd52cb7b362ccc22162f","tid":387808,"uid":87646,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"83-18=15?"},{"pid":"c3c518f8f02df92813219e104f27e42232224baf","tid":387808,"uid":92201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"以為買錯psp"},{"pid":"6899821188b4646616204dbeeb22a975914ba707","tid":387808,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以係用生果刀